data.enText: a large fish with silver skin and pink flesh that is used for food. Salmon live in the sea but swim up rivers to lay their eggs.

data.chText: 野生和人工养殖的鲑鱼

tr: any of various large food and game fishes of northern waters
usually migrate from salt to fresh water to spawn
flesh of any of various marine or freshwater fish of the family Salmonidae

value.def: A salmon is a large silver-coloured fish.

posc.def: Salmon is the pink flesh of this fish which is eaten as food. It is often smoked and eaten raw.

example.ex: ... a splendid lunch of smoked salmon.
